SlothBox is provided as a portfolio reference build. The cryptographic
primitives used (libsodium, age) are audited upstream, but the SlothBox
integration of those primitives has not been independently reviewed or
pen-tested as of v0.1.0-alpha.

DO NOT use SlothBox to transmit information whose disclosure could result
in loss of life, liberty, or significant financial harm UNTIL:

  1. v1.0.0 has been released, AND
  2. An independent cryptographic review has been published in this
     repository (see /audits/), AND
  3. You have read SECURITY.md and accept the documented threat model.

For high-stakes use cases, consider Signal, ProtonDrive, or Tresorit until
SlothBox completes external review.
